            </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
            <p>After being admitted, some universities may require their students to take a placement test for math, English,
                science, or for particular foreign languages. 
            </p>
            <p>You should examine your university’s admitted students’ page carefully
                to determine whether placement tests are necessary and to find out when and how to take them.</p>            </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
